headline: 3 Services Stocks in Hot Water
summary: Business services providers use their specialized expertise to help enterprises streamline operations and cut costs. But increasing competition from AI-driven upstarts has tempered enthusiasm, and over the past six months, the industry has pulled back by 2.4%. This drop was disappointing since the S&P 500 held its ground.
